<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Landscape"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Netflix原创动画『日本沈没2020』ED"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="景色"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="KAF"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="kaf"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="かふ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花譜"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花谱"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Magic"/><amll:meta key="album" value="魔法"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPZ922004452"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1501450522"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="001SM8jv2k4L6W"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="335546331"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="0d2IJAfQg8b2iMvda82KiT"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1688520975"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="4:14.320"><div begin="34.240" end="4:14.320"><p begin="34.240" end="40.280" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.240" end="34.470">カ</span><span begin="34.470" end="34.670">テ</span><span begin="34.670" end="34.870">ゴ</span><span begin="34.870" end="35.080">リ</span><span begin="35.080" end="35.310">っ</span><span begin="35.310" end="35.950">て</span><span begin="35.950" end="36.390">言</span><span begin="36.390" end="36.620">葉</span><span begin="36.620" end="37.000">が</span><span begin="37.660" end="37.840">も</span><span begin="37.840" end="38.090">は</span><span begin="38.090" end="38.370">や</span><span begin="38.490" end="38.960">呪</span><span begin="38.960" end="39.370">い</span><span begin="39.370" end="39.560">の</span><span begin="39.560" end="39.800">よ</span><span begin="39.800" end="40.000">う</span><span begin="40.000" end="40.280">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">「类别」这个词语已然形同诅咒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">「類別」這個詞語已然形同詛咒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The word category is already like a curse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">카테고리라는 단어가 이미 저주 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le mot catégorie semble déjà être une malédiction</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La palabra categoría ya parece una maldición</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Wort Kategorie ist schon fast wie ein Fluch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La parola categoria è ormai come una maledizione</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kategori tte kotoba ga mohaya noroi no you da</span></p><p begin="41.090" end="47.410" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.090" end="41.490">正</span><span begin="41.490" end="41.670">し</span><span begin="41.670" end="41.970">さ</span><span begin="41.970" end="42.320">を</span><span begin="42.790" end="43.260">証</span><span begin="43.260" end="43.880">明</span><span begin="43.880" end="44.020">で</span><span begin="44.120" end="44.730">き</span><span begin="44.730" end="45.160">る</span><span begin="45.380" end="45.610">は</span><span begin="45.610" end="46.080">ず</span><span begin="46.260" end="46.480">な</span><span begin="46.480" end="46.690">の</span><span begin="46.690" end="47.410">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明明本该能够证明其正确性</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">明明本該能夠證明其正確性</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even though it should be able to prove correctness</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">올바름을 증명할 수 있을 텐데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors qu&apos;il devrait pouvoir prouver la justesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque debería poder demostrar lo que es correcto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Obwohl es doch Richtigkeit beweisen sollte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Eppure dovrei poter dimostrare cosa è giusto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tadashisa o shoumei dekiru hazu na no ni</span></p><p begin="48.120" end="59.710" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.120" end="49.000">信</span><span begin="49.000" end="49.410">じ</span><span begin="49.410" end="49.890">き</span><span begin="49.890" end="50.320">れ</span><span begin="50.320" end="50.720">な</span><span begin="50.720" end="51.160">か</span><span begin="51.160" end="51.600">っ</span><span begin="51.600" end="52.330">た</span><span begin="52.910" end="53.310">未</span><span begin="53.310" end="53.740">来</span><span begin="53.740" end="54.290">が</span><span begin="54.980" end="55.900">通</span><span begin="55.900" end="56.300">り</span><span begin="56.710" end="57.180">過</span><span begin="57.180" end="57.490">ぎ</span><span begin="57.600" end="58.230">て</span><span begin="58.230" end="58.360">ゆ</span><span begin="58.470" end="59.710">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">未能完全相信的未来正擦肩而过</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">未能完全相信的未來正擦肩而過</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The future I couldn&apos;t fully believe in passes by</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끝내 믿지 못했던 미래가 스쳐 지나가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L&apos;avenir auquel je n&apos;ai pas pu croire entièrement passe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El futuro en el que no pude creer del todo está pasando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Zukunft an die ich nicht ganz glauben konnte zieht vorbei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il futuro in cui non sono riuscito a credere passa oltre</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinjikirenakatta mirai ga toorisugite yuku</span></p><p begin="1:01.630" end="1:04.280" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.630" end="1:01.890">世</span><span begin="1:01.890" end="1:02.310">界</span><span begin="1:02.310" end="1:02.510">が</span><span begin="1:02.510" end="1:03.120">涙</span><span begin="1:03.120" end="1:03.360">し</span><span begin="1:03.360" end="1:03.530">て</span><span begin="1:03.530" end="1:03.820">い</span><span begin="1:03.820" end="1:04.280">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">世界正在流泪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">世界正在流淚</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The world is in tears</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">세계가 눈물짓고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le monde pleure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El mundo está llorando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Welt weint</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il mondo sta piangendo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sekai ga namida shite iru</span></p><p begin="1:04.830" end="1:10.360" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:04.830" end="1:05.740">雫</span><span begin="1:05.740" end="1:06.170">に</span><span begin="1:06.170" end="1:06.570">飲</span><span begin="1:06.570" end="1:07.010">ま</span><span begin="1:07.010" end="1:07.330">れ</span><span begin="1:07.860" end="1:08.290">木</span><span begin="1:08.290" end="1:08.740">々</span><span begin="1:08.740" end="1:09.540">が</span><span begin="1:09.540" end="1:10.040">茂</span><span begin="1:10.040" end="1:10.360">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">树木饮下泪滴而愈发茂盛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">樹木飲下淚滴而愈發茂盛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Swallowed by drops the trees grow thick</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">물방울에 삼켜진 나무들이 우거져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Engloutis par les gouttes les arbres poussent à foison</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tragados por las gotas los árboles crecen espesos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Von Tropfen verschluckt wuchern die Bäume</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Inghiottiti dalle gocce gli alberi crescono fitti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shizuku ni nomare kigi ga shigeru</span></p><p begin="1:10.850" end="1:14.880" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.850" end="1:11.290">震</span><span begin="1:11.290" end="1:11.520">え</span><span begin="1:11.520" end="1:11.680">る</span><span begin="1:11.680" end="1:12.130">肌</span><span begin="1:12.130" end="1:12.470">を</span><span begin="1:12.750" end="1:13.010">世</span><span begin="1:13.010" end="1:13.430">界</span><span begin="1:13.430" end="1:13.660">は</span><span begin="1:13.660" end="1:13.890">待</span><span begin="1:13.890" end="1:14.080">っ</span><span begin="1:14.080" end="1:14.250">て</span><span begin="1:14.250" end="1:14.550">い</span><span begin="1:14.550" end="1:14.880">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">世界正等待着那颤抖的肌肤</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">世界正等待著那顫抖的肌膚</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The world is waiting for trembling skin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">떨리는 피부를 세계는 기다리고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le monde attend cette peau frissonnante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El mundo espera la piel temblorosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Welt wartet auf die zitternde Haut</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il mondo aspetta la pelle che trema</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Furueru hada o sekai wa matte iru</span></p><p begin="1:15.330" end="1:23.260" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:15.330" end="1:15.360">「</span><span begin="1:15.360" end="1:15.620">あ</span><span begin="1:15.620" end="1:15.810">る</span><span begin="1:15.810" end="1:16.000">べ</span><span begin="1:16.000" end="1:16.200">き</span><span begin="1:16.200" end="1:16.450">自</span><span begin="1:16.450" end="1:17.120">分</span><span begin="1:17.120" end="1:17.150">」</span><span begin="1:17.150" end="1:17.660">を</span><span begin="1:18.560" end="1:18.870">決</span><span begin="1:19.040" end="1:19.440">め</span><span begin="1:19.440" end="1:19.780">つ</span><span begin="1:19.880" end="1:20.300">け</span><span begin="1:20.300" end="1:20.730">る</span><span begin="1:20.730" end="1:21.570">必</span><span begin="1:21.570" end="1:22.040">要</span><span begin="1:22.040" end="1:22.450">は</span><span begin="1:22.450" end="1:22.660">な</span><span begin="1:22.660" end="1:22.850">い</span><span begin="1:22.850" end="1:23.260">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">没必要去断定「理应成为的自己」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">沒必要去斷定「理應成為的自己」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">There is no need to define &quot;the self you should be&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">「있어야 할 자신」을 단정 지을 필요는 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">« Il n&apos;y a pas besoin de définir ce que l&apos;on devrait être »</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No hay necesidad de imponer «el yo que debería ser»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es ist nicht nötig festzulegen „wer man sein sollte“</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non c&apos;è bisogno di decidere «chi dovresti essere»</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Arubeki jibun&quot; o kimetsukeru hitsuyou wa nai sa</span></p><p begin="1:24.150" end="1:27.520" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:24.150" end="1:24.440">な</span><span begin="1:24.440" end="1:24.590">ん</span><span begin="1:24.590" end="1:24.850">だ</span><span begin="1:24.850" end="1:25.020">っ</span><span begin="1:25.020" end="1:25.650">て</span><span begin="1:25.650" end="1:25.880">で</span><span begin="1:25.880" end="1:26.150">き</span><span begin="1:26.150" end="1:27.520">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">什么都能做到</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">什麼都能做到</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We can do anything</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">뭐든지 할 수 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">On peut tout faire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Podemos hacer cualquier cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir können alles tun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Possiamo fare qualsiasi cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nandatte dekiru</span></p><p begin="1:28.020" end="1:34.380" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:28.020" end="1:28.860">僕</span><span begin="1:28.860" end="1:29.310">ら</span><span begin="1:29.310" end="1:30.270">は</span><span begin="1:30.820" end="1:31.010">ど</span><span begin="1:31.010" end="1:31.470">こ</span><span begin="1:31.470" end="1:31.860">に</span><span begin="1:31.860" end="1:32.110">だ</span><span begin="1:32.110" end="1:32.300">っ</span><span begin="1:32.300" end="1:32.720">て</span><span begin="1:32.720" end="1:33.150">行</span><span begin="1:33.150" end="1:33.390">け</span><span begin="1:33.390" end="1:34.380">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们无论哪里都能到达</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們無論哪裡都能到達</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We can go anywhere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들은 어디로든 갈 수 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous pouvons aller n&apos;importe où</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nosotros podemos ir a cualquier parte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir können überallhin gehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Noi possiamo andare ovunque</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa doko ni datte ikeru</span></p><p begin="1:34.870" end="1:42.140" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.870" end="1:35.740">僕</span><span begin="1:35.740" end="1:36.140">ら</span><span begin="1:36.140" end="1:36.970">は</span><span begin="1:37.650" end="1:37.850">ど</span><span begin="1:37.850" end="1:38.320">こ</span><span begin="1:38.320" end="1:38.730">に</span><span begin="1:38.730" end="1:38.970">だ</span><span begin="1:38.970" end="1:39.140">っ</span><span begin="1:39.140" end="1:39.590">て</span><span begin="1:39.590" end="1:40.000">飛</span><span begin="1:40.000" end="1:40.240">べ</span><span begin="1:40.240" end="1:42.140">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们无论哪里都能飞去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們無論哪裡都能飛去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We can fly anywhere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들은 어디로든 날 수 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous pouvons voler n&apos;importe où</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nosotros podemos volar a cualquier parte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir können überallhin fliegen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Noi possiamo volare ovunque</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa doko ni datte toberu</span></p><p begin="1:42.760" end="1:49.100" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:42.760" end="1:42.870">不</span><span begin="1:42.970" end="1:43.660">変</span><span begin="1:43.660" end="1:44.250">で</span><span begin="1:44.250" end="1:44.520">い</span><span begin="1:44.520" end="1:45.150">る</span><span begin="1:45.150" end="1:45.390">の</span><span begin="1:45.390" end="1:45.610">は</span><span begin="1:46.030" end="1:46.880">僕</span><span begin="1:46.880" end="1:47.100">が</span><span begin="1:47.100" end="1:47.960">僕</span><span begin="1:47.960" end="1:48.580">だ</span><span begin="1:48.580" end="1:48.830">か</span><span begin="1:48.830" end="1:49.100">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">保持不变是因为我就是我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">保持不變是因為我就是我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What remains unchanging is that I am me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">변하지 않는 건 내가 나이기 때문이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce qui reste immuable c&apos;est que je suis moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sigo siendo inmutable porque yo soy yo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was unveränderlich bleibt ist dass ich ich bin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se resto immutato è perché io sono io</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fuhen de iru no wa boku ga boku dakara</span></p><p begin="1:49.840" end="1:55.060" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:49.840" end="1:50.270">景</span><span begin="1:50.270" end="1:51.140">色</span><span begin="1:51.140" end="1:51.560">を</span><span begin="1:51.560" end="1:52.000">抱</span><span begin="1:52.000" end="1:52.390">き</span><span begin="1:52.390" end="1:53.090">し</span><span begin="1:53.090" end="1:53.300">め</span><span begin="1:53.300" end="1:55.060">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">拥抱这片景色</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">擁抱這片景色</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Embracing the scenery</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">경치를 끌어안고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Enlaçant le paysage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Abrazando el paisaje</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Landschaft umarmend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Abbracciando il paesaggio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Keshiki o dakishimete</span></p><p begin="1:56.730" end="2:00.600" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:56.730" end="1:57.400">僕</span><span begin="1:57.400" end="1:57.890">は</span><span begin="1:59.080" end="1:59.320">自</span><span begin="1:59.320" end="2:00.180">由</span><span begin="2:00.180" end="2:00.600">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我是自由的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我是自由的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I am free</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 자유야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je suis libre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo soy libre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bin ich frei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io sono libero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku wa jiyuu da</span></p><p begin="2:13.610" end="2:19.790" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:13.610" end="2:14.070">歩</span><span begin="2:14.070" end="2:14.290">き</span><span begin="2:14.290" end="2:14.450">出</span><span begin="2:14.450" end="2:14.700">す</span><span begin="2:14.700" end="2:15.140">こ</span><span begin="2:15.140" end="2:15.390">と</span><span begin="2:15.390" end="2:16.150">に</span><span begin="2:17.120" end="2:17.320">理</span><span begin="2:17.320" end="2:17.740">由</span><span begin="2:17.740" end="2:17.950">な</span><span begin="2:17.950" end="2:18.160">ん</span><span begin="2:18.160" end="2:18.610">て</span><span begin="2:18.610" end="2:18.820">い</span><span begin="2:18.820" end="2:19.030">ら</span><span begin="2:19.030" end="2:19.230">な</span><span begin="2:19.230" end="2:19.450">い</span><span begin="2:19.450" end="2:19.790">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">迈出脚步其实不需要什么理由</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">邁出腳步其實不需要什麼理由</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You don&apos;t need a reason to start walking but</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">걸어 나가는 데에 이유 따윈 필요 없지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">On n&apos;a pas besoin de raison pour commencer à marcher mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No se necesita ninguna razón para empezar a caminar pero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es braucht keinen Grund um loszugehen aber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non serve alcun motivo per iniziare a camminare ma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Arukidasu koto ni riyuu nante iranai ga</span></p><p begin="2:20.500" end="2:24.960" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:20.500" end="2:20.710">い</span><span begin="2:20.710" end="2:20.940">つ</span><span begin="2:20.940" end="2:21.140">だ</span><span begin="2:21.140" end="2:21.360">っ</span><span begin="2:21.360" end="2:21.580">て</span><span begin="2:21.580" end="2:21.800">固</span><span begin="2:21.800" end="2:22.240">定</span><span begin="2:22.240" end="2:22.670">概</span><span begin="2:22.670" end="2:23.080">念</span><span begin="2:23.080" end="2:23.290">が</span><span begin="2:23.290" end="2:23.520">邪</span><span begin="2:23.520" end="2:23.740">魔</span><span begin="2:23.740" end="2:24.120">を</span><span begin="2:24.120" end="2:24.380">す</span><span begin="2:24.380" end="2:24.960">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">固有观念却总是来碍事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">固有觀念卻總是來礙事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Stereotypes always get in the way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">언제나 고정관념이 방해를 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les idées fixes se mettent toujours en travers</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Los estereotipos siempre se interponen en el camino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Immer stehen feste Vorstellungen im Weg</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">I preconcetti sono sempre d&apos;intralcio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsu datte koteigainen ga jama o suru</span></p><p begin="2:27.340" end="2:39.420" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:27.340" end="2:27.600">し</span><span begin="2:27.600" end="2:27.780">か</span><span begin="2:27.780" end="2:28.240">し</span><span begin="2:28.240" end="2:29.140">涙</span><span begin="2:29.140" end="2:29.970">を</span><span begin="2:30.590" end="2:31.010">打</span><span begin="2:31.010" end="2:31.430">ち</span><span begin="2:31.430" end="2:32.290">払</span><span begin="2:32.290" end="2:32.730">う</span><span begin="2:32.730" end="2:33.030">の</span><span begin="2:33.170" end="2:33.590">も</span><span begin="2:33.590" end="2:33.880">い</span><span begin="2:33.990" end="2:34.440">つ</span><span begin="2:34.440" end="2:34.670">だ</span><span begin="2:34.670" end="2:34.870">っ</span><span begin="2:34.870" end="2:35.200">て</span><span begin="2:35.680" end="2:36.160">そ</span><span begin="2:36.160" end="2:36.600">こ</span><span begin="2:36.600" end="2:37.060">に</span><span begin="2:37.060" end="2:37.470">あ</span><span begin="2:37.470" end="2:37.640">る</span><span begin="2:37.640" end="2:37.850">景</span><span begin="2:37.850" end="2:38.300">色</span><span begin="2:38.300" end="2:39.420">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但拂去泪水的也总是那里的景色</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但拂去淚水的也總是那裡的景色</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">But what brushes away the tears is always the scenery right there</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하지만 눈물을 떨쳐내는 것도 언제나 그곳에 있는 경치야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais ce qui balaie les larmes c&apos;est toujours le paysage qui se trouve là</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sin embargo lo que ahuyenta las lágrimas es siempre el paisaje que está ahí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aber was die Tränen vertreibt ist auch immer die Landschaft die dort ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tuttavia a spazzare via le lacrime è sempre il paesaggio che si trova lì</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shikashi namida o uchiharau no mo itsu datte soko ni aru keshiki da</span></p><p begin="2:41.050" end="2:42.000" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.050" end="2:41.300">綺</span><span begin="2:41.300" end="2:41.710">麗</span><span begin="2:41.710" end="2:42.000">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真美啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真美啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아름다워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est beau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Es hermoso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sie ist wunderschön</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È bellissimo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kirei da</span></p><p begin="2:44.500" end="2:45.610" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:44.500" end="2:44.740">綺</span><span begin="2:44.740" end="2:45.140">麗</span><span begin="2:45.140" end="2:45.370">だ</span><span begin="2:45.370" end="2:45.610">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真美啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真美啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It is so beautiful</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아름답구나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est vraiment beau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Qué hermoso es</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wirklich wunderschön</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È proprio bellissimo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kirei da na</span></p><p begin="2:47.760" end="2:52.350" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:47.760" end="2:48.610">蠢</span><span begin="2:48.610" end="2:48.990">く</span><span begin="2:49.420" end="2:50.310">風</span><span begin="2:50.310" end="2:50.690">が</span><span begin="2:51.160" end="2:52.030">愛</span><span begin="2:52.030" end="2:52.350">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">躁动的微风与爱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">躁動的微風與愛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The writhing wind and love</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">꿈틀대는 바람이 사랑이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le vent qui s&apos;agite et l&apos;amour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El viento que se agita el amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der wimmelnde Wind die Liebe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il vento che si agita l&apos;amore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ugomeku kaze ga ai ga</span></p><p begin="2:54.550" end="3:00.080" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:54.550" end="2:55.430">肌</span><span begin="2:55.430" end="2:55.720">を</span><span begin="2:55.880" end="2:56.100">撫</span><span begin="2:56.100" end="2:56.320">で</span><span begin="2:56.320" end="2:56.900">る</span><span begin="2:57.960" end="2:58.300">過</span><span begin="2:58.410" end="2:58.770">去</span><span begin="2:58.880" end="2:59.280">の</span><span begin="2:59.280" end="2:59.710">声</span><span begin="2:59.710" end="3:00.080">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">抚过肌肤的过去的声音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">撫過肌膚的過去的聲音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The voices of the past stroking my skin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">피부를 어루만지는 과거의 목소리가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les voix du passé qui caressent la peau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las voces del pasado que acarician la piel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Stimmen der Vergangenheit die die Haut streicheln</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le voci del passato che accarezzano la pelle</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hada o naderu kako no koe ga</span></p><p begin="3:00.780" end="3:05.210" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:00.780" end="3:01.240">僕</span><span begin="3:01.240" end="3:01.450">ら</span><span begin="3:01.450" end="3:01.620">の</span><span begin="3:01.620" end="3:01.880">背</span><span begin="3:01.880" end="3:02.300">中</span><span begin="3:02.300" end="3:02.530">を</span><span begin="3:02.530" end="3:02.930">叩</span><span begin="3:02.930" end="3:03.150">い</span><span begin="3:03.150" end="3:03.590">て</span><span begin="3:03.590" end="3:04.000">笑</span><span begin="3:04.000" end="3:05.210">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">拍着我们的后背微笑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">拍著我們的後背微笑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Slap our backs and laugh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들의 등을 두드리며 웃어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tapent dans nos dos en riant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nos palmean la espalda y ríen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Klopfen uns auf den Rücken und lachen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ci battono sulla schiena e ridono</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura no senaka o tataite warau</span></p><p begin="3:08.310" end="3:13.760" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:08.310" end="3:08.730">理</span><span begin="3:08.730" end="3:08.940">由</span><span begin="3:08.940" end="3:09.160">な</span><span begin="3:09.160" end="3:09.480">き</span><span begin="3:10.020" end="3:11.290">礎</span><span begin="3:11.290" end="3:11.510">に</span><span begin="3:11.510" end="3:11.740">な</span><span begin="3:11.740" end="3:13.760">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">成为毫无理由的基石</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">成為毫無理由的基石</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Becoming a foundation without reason</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이유 없는 주춧돌이 돼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Deviennent des fondations sans raison</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se convierten en cimientos sin razón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Werden zum grundlosen Fundament</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Diventano fondamenta senza motivo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Wake naki ishizue ni naru</span></p><p begin="3:14.270" end="3:20.660" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:14.270" end="3:15.170">僕</span><span begin="3:15.170" end="3:15.560">ら</span><span begin="3:15.560" end="3:16.570">は</span><span begin="3:17.110" end="3:17.310">ど</span><span begin="3:17.310" end="3:17.740">こ</span><span begin="3:17.740" end="3:18.150">に</span><span begin="3:18.150" end="3:18.390">だ</span><span begin="3:18.390" end="3:18.590">っ</span><span begin="3:18.590" end="3:19.050">て</span><span begin="3:19.050" end="3:19.440">行</span><span begin="3:19.440" end="3:19.690">け</span><span begin="3:19.690" end="3:20.660">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们无论哪里都能到达</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們無論哪裡都能到達</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We can go anywhere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들은 어디로든 갈 수 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous pouvons aller n&apos;importe où</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nosotros podemos ir a cualquier parte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir können überallhin gehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Noi possiamo andare ovunque</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa doko ni datte ikeru</span></p><p begin="3:21.140" end="3:27.740" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:21.140" end="3:22.030">僕</span><span begin="3:22.030" end="3:22.440">ら</span><span begin="3:22.440" end="3:23.440">は</span><span begin="3:23.960" end="3:24.140">ど</span><span begin="3:24.140" end="3:24.630">こ</span><span begin="3:24.630" end="3:25.010">に</span><span begin="3:25.010" end="3:25.240">だ</span><span begin="3:25.240" end="3:25.440">っ</span><span begin="3:25.440" end="3:25.880">て</span><span begin="3:25.880" end="3:26.320">飛</span><span begin="3:26.320" end="3:26.530">べ</span><span begin="3:26.530" end="3:27.740">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们无论哪里都能飞去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們無論哪裡都能飛去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We can fly anywhere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들은 어디로든 날 수 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous pouvons voler n&apos;importe où</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nosotros podemos volar a cualquier parte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir können überallhin fliegen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Noi possiamo volare ovunque</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa doko ni datte toberu</span></p><p begin="3:28.810" end="3:35.200" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:28.810" end="3:29.660">仮</span><span begin="3:29.660" end="3:29.840">初</span><span begin="3:29.960" end="3:30.620">め</span><span begin="3:30.620" end="3:31.040">の</span><span begin="3:31.040" end="3:31.370">意</span><span begin="3:31.470" end="3:31.640">味</span><span begin="3:31.640" end="3:32.140">を</span><span begin="3:32.680" end="3:33.580">全</span><span begin="3:33.580" end="3:33.970">て</span><span begin="3:33.970" end="3:34.180">捨</span><span begin="3:34.180" end="3:34.330">て</span><span begin="3:34.440" end="3:34.640">て</span><span begin="3:34.640" end="3:34.880">い</span><span begin="3:34.880" end="3:35.200">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">抛弃所有虚假的意义吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">拋棄所有虛假的意義吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Throw away all the temporary meanings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">덧없는 의미를 전부 버리고 가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Jette toutes ces significations éphémères</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Desecha todos los significados efímeros</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wirf all die vorläufigen Bedeutungen weg</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Getta via tutti i significati effimeri</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Karisome no imi o subete sutete ike</span></p><p begin="3:35.700" end="3:41.170" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:35.700" end="3:36.150">朝</span><span begin="3:36.150" end="3:36.750">は</span><span begin="3:37.880" end="3:38.300">何</span><span begin="3:38.300" end="3:38.730">度</span><span begin="3:38.730" end="3:38.960">だ</span><span begin="3:38.960" end="3:39.160">っ</span><span begin="3:39.160" end="3:39.580">て</span><span begin="3:39.580" end="3:40.240">巡</span><span begin="3:40.240" end="3:41.170">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">清晨无论多少次都会降临</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">清晨無論多少次都會降臨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Morning will come around countless times</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아침은 몇 번이고 돌아와</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le matin reviendra maintes et maintes fois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La mañana regresa una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der Morgen kehrt immer wieder zurück</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il mattino ritorna infinite volte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Asa wa nando datte meguru</span></p><p begin="3:41.720" end="3:48.100" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:41.720" end="3:42.600">僕</span><span begin="3:42.600" end="3:42.990">ら</span><span begin="3:42.990" end="3:43.830">は</span><span begin="3:44.500" end="3:44.700">ど</span><span begin="3:44.700" end="3:45.160">こ</span><span begin="3:45.160" end="3:45.580">に</span><span begin="3:45.580" end="3:45.820">だ</span><span begin="3:45.820" end="3:46.010">っ</span><span begin="3:46.010" end="3:46.420">て</span><span begin="3:46.420" end="3:46.860">行</span><span begin="3:46.860" end="3:47.090">け</span><span begin="3:47.090" end="3:48.100">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们无论哪里都能到达</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們無論哪裡都能到達</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We can go anywhere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들은 어디로든 갈 수 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous pouvons aller n&apos;importe où</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nosotros podemos ir a cualquier parte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir können überallhin gehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Noi possiamo andare ovunque</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa doko ni datte ikeru</span></p><p begin="3:48.570" end="3:55.440" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:48.570" end="3:49.460">僕</span><span begin="3:49.460" end="3:49.870">ら</span><span begin="3:49.870" end="3:50.840">は</span><span begin="3:51.380" end="3:51.570">ど</span><span begin="3:51.570" end="3:52.020">こ</span><span begin="3:52.020" end="3:52.430">に</span><span begin="3:52.430" end="3:52.660">だ</span><span begin="3:52.660" end="3:52.860">っ</span><span begin="3:52.860" end="3:53.290">て</span><span begin="3:53.290" end="3:53.720">飛</span><span begin="3:53.720" end="3:53.970">べ</span><span begin="3:53.970" end="3:55.440">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们无论哪里都能飞去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們無論哪裡都能飛去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We can fly anywhere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들은 어디로든 날 수 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous pouvons voler n&apos;importe où</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nosotros podemos volar a cualquier parte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir können überallhin fliegen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Noi possiamo volare ovunque</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa doko ni datte toberu</span></p><p begin="3:56.420" end="4:02.800" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:56.420" end="3:56.710">そ</span><span begin="3:56.710" end="3:56.910">の</span><span begin="3:56.910" end="3:57.370">全</span><span begin="3:57.370" end="3:57.600">て</span><span begin="3:57.600" end="3:57.960">に</span><span begin="3:57.960" end="3:59.090">命</span><span begin="3:59.090" end="3:59.320">を</span><span begin="3:59.730" end="4:00.140">か</span><span begin="4:00.140" end="4:00.590">け</span><span begin="4:00.590" end="4:01.000">る</span><span begin="4:01.000" end="4:01.410">価</span><span begin="4:01.410" end="4:01.850">値</span><span begin="4:01.850" end="4:02.050">が</span><span begin="4:02.050" end="4:02.320">あ</span><span begin="4:02.320" end="4:02.800">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那一切都值得倾注生命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那一切都值得傾注生命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">All of it is worth risking our lives for</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 모든 것에 목숨을 걸 가치가 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tout cela vaut la peine d&apos;y risquer sa vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Todo eso vale la pena para arriesgar la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">All das ist es wert sein Leben dafür einzusetzen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tutto questo ha il valore di scommetterci la vita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono subete ni inochi o kakeru kachi ga aru</span></p><p begin="4:03.560" end="4:08.830" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:03.560" end="4:03.980">景</span><span begin="4:03.980" end="4:04.880">色</span><span begin="4:04.880" end="4:05.300">を</span><span begin="4:05.300" end="4:05.720">抱</span><span begin="4:05.720" end="4:06.120">き</span><span begin="4:06.120" end="4:06.790">し</span><span begin="4:06.790" end="4:07.020">め</span><span begin="4:07.020" end="4:08.830">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">拥抱这片景色</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">擁抱這片景色</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Embracing the scenery</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">경치를 끌어안고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Enlaçant le paysage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Abrazando el paisaje</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Landschaft umarmend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Abbracciando il paesaggio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Keshiki o dakishimete</span></p><p begin="4:10.450" end="4:14.320" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:10.450" end="4:11.110">僕</span><span begin="4:11.110" end="4:11.970">は</span><span begin="4:12.740" end="4:13.050">自</span><span begin="4:13.050" end="4:13.880">由</span><span begin="4:13.880" end="4:14.320">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我是自由的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我是自由的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I am free</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 자유야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je suis libre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo soy libre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bin ich frei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io sono libero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku wa jiyuu da</span></p></div></body></tt>